review_title: These socks are definitely worth buying!
reviews:
I am a young 62 and i love these socks!! They are so soft and comfy, i’m wearing them around the clock now!
Try these, you won’t be sorry.
OK, this is an update, i am now wearing the next size up, meaning the largest size of these socks and they are a much better fit.
Unless you have teensy feet, try the bigger size.
